rComments: Loved her class, she was awesome. She tended to read off her slides but when it comes to exam, you have to know everything accurately (all lecture slides). She tends to focus on MC, short answer and one long answer. If you know your material throughly, you should be fine. Overall, was an interesting course.

Prof pretty must just reads off lecture notes.  Speaks too quietly, and you must go to lecture because there is no textbook for the course.  Short answers are unfair. Overall, stay away from this course because it's not required for any program.
